    /_/        x-projetion.org

usage: main.py [-h] -f INPUT_FILE -l LINES_PER_FILE

File Splitter by Lines

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -f INPUT_FILE, --files INPUT_FILE
                        Input file name
  -l LINES_PER_FILE, --lines LINES_PER_FILE
                        Number of lines per file
```
